
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Yes' radio button from Contrast enhanced box on Page 03
And	I go to Page 06 of Thoracic MRT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Pleural effusion' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

And 'Biconvex' radio button is enabled
And 'Concave' radio button is enabled

And 'Free flow' radio button is enabled
And 'Interlobal' radio button is enabled

And 'Transudate' radio button is enabled
And 'Exsudate' radio button is enabled
And 'Hematothorax' radio button is enabled
And 'Chylothorax' radio button is enabled
And 'Empyema' radio button is enabled

And 'Sedimentation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Split pleura sign' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Right' radio button
Then 'Max. width' input field is enabled

When I select 'Left' radio button
Then 'Max. width' input field is enabled

When I select 'Hematothorax' radio button
Then 'Coagulum' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Chylothorax' radio button
Then 'T1w hyperintense' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Empyema' radio button
Then 'Contrast-enhancing capsule' checkbox is enabled
And 'Focal signal voids' checkbox is enabled
